OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry and bright start but soon
OL,6,Fturning cloudier as rain and drizzle
OL,7,Fspreads northwards in the morning. A
OL,8,Fcloudy afternoon with outbreaks of
OL,9,Frain, some heavy, continuing to move
OL,10,Fnorthwards, clearing the area later..
OL,11,FBreezy around the coast.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA largely dry night in the
OL,14,Feast with late bright spells in the
OL,15,Fevening, and clear spells overnight.
OL,16,FCloudier in the west with a few
OL,17,Fshowers possible. Breezier overnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
