OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FA dry morning with bright or
OL,6,Fsunny spells. Bright spells continuing
OL,7,Fthrough the afternoon but a few
OL,8,Fshowers developing. Windy at times.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FCloudy
OL,11,Fand breezy on Saturday with heavy
OL,12,Fshowers clearing later in the day. Dry
OL,13,Fon Sunday and Monday with sunny
OL,14,Fspells, but possibly cloudier towards
OL,15,Fthe coasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
